itkwasm-dicom
=======

> Read files and images related to DICOM file format.

[![itkwasm-dicom version](https://badge.fury.io/py/itkwasm_dicom.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/itkwasm_dicom/)

## Installation

```shell
pip install itkwasm-dicom
```
